{"tid":596540,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X 也能破解！破解iOS密碼工具GrayKey正式推出！","createTime":"2018-03-17T17:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T14:56:10.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"77b043e15eb478f636ad8cae78d63b8a33ca5d75","tid":596540,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:49:04.000Z","msg":"iPhone 安全程度極高，甚至連美國 FBI（Federal Bureau of Investigation、聯邦調查局）從 iPhone 搜証時，也要交由以色列 Cellebrite 公司代為破解 iPhone 密碼，才可從手機中取得關鍵証據。近期網上流傳 1 款由 Grayshift 公司製造的 GrayKey 工具，據知能夠破解連同 iPhone X 在內的最新版本 iPhone，但官網上未有提供相關裝置的圖片和資料。直至最近，Malwarebytes LABS 才公布 GrayKey 工具的相關相片和資料。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2030000/2032115/1023webcrackiphone01_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2030000%2F2032115%2F1023webcrackiphone01_600.jpg&h=18184dd7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nGrayKey 是 1 個灰色盒子，盒子設有兩條 Lightning 線，可同時連接兩部 iPhone 進行破解。當 iPhone 連接 GrayKey 後，GrayKey 會不斷猜測 iPhone 的密碼。不過，即使是 6 個位的密碼，其破解仍可能需要長達 3 天或以上。當裝置破解後，iPhone 內的完整資料會傳送至 GrayKey 裝置內，用戶可透過網頁介面連接 GrayKey，下載相關資料進行分析。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2030000/2032115/1023webcrackiphone04_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2030000%2F2032115%2F1023webcrackiphone04_1024.jpg&h=3019b812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2032115/iPhone%20X%20%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%81%E9%9A%A8%E8%BA%AB%20iPhone%20%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3%E8%A3%9D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9C%9F%E8%BA%AB%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2032115%2FiPhone%2520X%2520%25E4%25B9%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A7%25A3%25EF%25BC%2581%25E9%259A%25A8%25E8%25BA%25AB%2520iPhone%2520%25E5%25AF%2586%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25A3%259D%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%259C%259F%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589&d=nFg6TccAYbkpsrEucg2bMsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a91b4373\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2032115/iPhone%20X%20%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%81%E9%9A%A8%E8%BA%AB%20iPhone%20%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3%E8%A3%9D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9C%9F%E8%BA%AB%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89</a></div>"},{"pid":"d561539c066cda4075826ac74952bc0fdcccdd86","tid":596540,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:49:55.000Z","msg":"GrayKey 分設 15,000 美元（折合約 HK$117,647）和 30,000 美元（折合約 HK$235,294）兩種購買模式，其中 15,000 美元版本必須長期連接互聯網才可使用，而且只可使用 300 次。至於 30,000 美元的版本，只要經互聯網完成啟用程序後，即可無限次離線使用。裝置的體積只有約 101.6mm x 101.6mm x 50.8mm，體積相當細小，易於隨身攜帶。雖然 GrayKey 或許有助警方打擊罪案，但若然 GrayKey 被不法分子購買或竊去，或會提高 iPhone 用戶的私隱外洩風險。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2030000/2032115/1023webcrackiphone03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2030000%2F2032115%2F1023webcrackiphone03_600.jpg&h=f423d348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">從操作介面中，可見 iPhone X 也可被 GrayKey 裝置破解。</span></div>"},{"pid":"eac25096fecd73b895df0dbb931959ea99a4873d","tid":596540,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:23:51.000Z","msg":"太麻煩唔計數"},{"pid":"9e2c48733e900b8eeface3171e723e4cae7c1256","tid":596540,"uid":2300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:29:38.000Z","msg":"先達佬成日收lock機仲唔發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe40d03d5032ba54ebb91f83a6672be4a551732f","tid":596540,"uid":5846,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"p